Microstructures of the AlxCrNbTiVZr (x=0 (a, b); 0.25 (c, d); 0.5 (e, f); 1 (g, h)) alloys after annealing at 1200°C: a, c, e, g – SEM-BSE images, b, d, f, h – EBSD phase maps. The bcc phase is identified with the red color on phase maps, C15 Laves phase is identified with the green color, and C14 Laves phase – with the yellow color.
